==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whiteweed
<hw>White"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A perennial composite herb (<spn>Chrysanthemum Leucanthemum</spn>)
with conspicuous white rays and a yellow disk, a common weed in grass
lands and pastures; -- called also <altname>oxeye
daisy</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whitewing</ent>⟦br⟧
